data.actual_result: A new category appears in the end of the list showing as "Uncategorized"
data.expected_result: The available selectable channel categories are shown only
data.short_description: Muting a channel adds a new channel category in the end of the categories list appearing as "Uncategorized"
data.steps_to_repro: - Be in a server with permission to edit the category of a channel - Mute the channel - Open the channel category drop down - Look at the end of the channel categories list
